# Christmas for Kids - Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# NEVER commit .env to version control!
#
# ENVIRONMENT-SPECIFIC FILES:
# - .env              (local development - gitignored)
# - .env.staging      (staging deployment - gitignored, read-only)
# - .env.production   (production deployment - gitignored, read-only)
#
# The .env.staging and .env.production files are marked READ-ONLY (chmod 444)
# to prevent accidental edits. To update them:
#   chmod 644 .env.production  # Make writable
#   vim .env.production        # Edit the file
#   chmod 444 .env.production  # Make read-only again
#
# PROTECTION MECHANISM:
# - These files are in .gitignore (never pushed to GitHub)
# - Safe cleanup: git clean -fd (ignores .gitignore files) ✅
# - Or use: scripts/safe-cleanup.sh (prompts before deleting)
# - NEVER use: git clean -fdx (deletes .gitignore files!) ❌
#
# These files persist across all branches (gitignored = stays in working directory)

# ====================
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (.env)
# ====================
# Copy this section to .env for local Docker development

# Database Configuration for Docker
DB_HOST=db
DB_NAME=cfk_sponsorship_dev
DB_USER=cfk_user
DB_PASSWORD=cfk_pass

# SMTP Configuration - optional for local dev
SMTP_USERNAME=
SMTP_PASSWORD=

# Application Settings
APP_DEBUG=true
BASE_URL=http://localhost:8082
ENVIRONMENT=local

# ====================
